### My Exercise Solution

Here is the code for the `main.tf` file I used to create AWS infrastructure with Terraform:

```bash
provider "aws" {
  access_key = "<Your Access Key>"
  secret_key = "<Your Secret Key>"
  region = "us-east-1"
}

resource "aws_instance" "Udacity" {
  count = "2"
  ami = "ami-0323c3dd2da7fb37d"
  instance_type = "t2.small"
  tags = {
    name = "Udacity Terraform"
  }
}
``` 

### AWS Costs Reminder

Please verify you have destroyed the infrastructure you created in this lesson.
